name: Membership Registration Reports
query:
SELECT 
    name AS "ID No.",
    date as "Date",
    customer_name AS "Customer Name:Data:190",
    district_name AS "District Name",
    village AS "Village",
    mobile_no AS "Mobile:Data:100",
    family_no AS "Family No.",
    registrated_by as "Registrated By"
    
FROM  
    `tabMembership Registration`
WHERE 
    date BETWEEN %(from)s AND %(to)s
